title: Alejandro Maurtua’s CV
text:
Business Finance student with Minor in Data Science.

alejandromaurtuap@gmail.com | My LinkedIn





Idaho Entrepeneur - Rexburg, ID - April 2024 - July 2024
• Managed and cleaned data gathered by the project team to create competitive analysis reports comparing 20+ competitors from a new Chocolate business • Performed a Chocolate Taste test event and designed a professional questionnaire to compare the business product with 5 competitive brands • Analyzed and organized 180+ pages of data gathered from the Chocolate Taste test questionnaires to build visuals using PowerBI and provide insights and recommendations



BYU-I - Rexburg, ID - June 2022 - Current
• Supervised and organized data from Business and Computer Science professionals applying for the Online Grader position using Microsoft Excel, Trello, Tableau, Workday, and BYU-I Management websites • Analyzed application documents including University/Master’s transcripts for 100+ applicants each semester • Reviewed Digital Interviews from most qualified applicants to make final hiring decisions to fill out +15 vacancies each semester • Created final KPI reports using Microsoft Excel and compared performance with previous semesters




2022-2026 BYU-Idaho, Rexburg.



3.8



Current BYU-I Scholarship
